{"tid":1411893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎大家打去天水圍管理處","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:05:12.000Z","uid":271627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3a185b354b3f766057e17d24646df4447962c1","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"琴晚天水圍咁多軍狗<br />\n點解狗屋附近d屋苑全部都有軍狗入到去拉人<br />\n而屋苑管理處無人理<br />\n公屋 居屋 私樓全部都係<br />\n歡迎大家齊齊打去管理處問以後點保障附近居民的安全<br />\n依家係咪夜晚落街散步都唔得呀？"},{"pid":"a14032fd1f10c7ab4bfdc993c925cb8f3c10d0e9","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd3a185b354b3f766057e17d24646df4447962c1","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"琴晚天水圍咁多軍狗<br />\n點解狗屋附近d屋苑全部都有軍狗入到去拉人<br />\n而屋苑管理處無人理<br />\n公屋 居屋 私樓全部都係<br />\n歡迎大家齊齊打去管理處問以後點保障附近居民的安全<br />\n依家係咪夜晚落街散步都唔得呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"天耀 24481810<br />\n天盛 22542000"},{"pid":"3e1958bcc27992a6e693de21be664abc6caf5032","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n再推一推<br />\n<br />\n今日再次天水圍有場<br />\n但上述屋苑第二次放狗入黎<br />\n唔夠廿四小時內兩次軍狗入屋苑<br />\n就算過左今日 好快都會有天水圍場<br />\n想大家完左今日之後<br />\n有時間就幫手打去上述屋苑 <br />\n要求佢地唔俾軍狗擅闖私人地方"},{"pid":"2b23bbcf0034b1b3af1b2e100738f0e98b73167c","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"67f9d4b8a8519a38f3f735d0232f28b397722a58","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"792f792ed96b7676bce6dafb1594e8199de9e044","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a47ed90f44be26aab8df940df0c6757d40b79929","tid":1411893,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">所有啟勝管理嘅屋苑都應該問吓自己管理處 </span>"},{"pid":"75e967c2d6740dc34784c4dc93a1327148a07842","tid":1411893,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a47ed90f44be26aab8df940df0c6757d40b79929","tid":1411893,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">所有啟勝管理嘅屋苑都應該問吓自己管理處 </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"召喚所有啟勝管理嘅居苑住戶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaishing.hk%2Fresident%2Fkaishing%2Fcontact_us.do%3Fcompany%3Dkaishing&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=97d48680\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing</a><br />\n<br />\n本人想查詢啟勝對近日示威事件之處理手法。<br />\n昨日天盛苑（同屬啟勝管理）管理員肆意讓警察進入屋苑範圍內，更任由警員在內施放催淚彈、妄顧居民安全。<br />\n本人不希望同類事情發生於本屋苑範圍內，希望貴公司能及早計劃對策，妥善處理應否讓警員在沒有搜查令之下進入本苑。"},{"pid":"661c81aeb9427054de0f9010290565c75b450777","tid":1411893,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e967c2d6740dc34784c4dc93a1327148a07842","tid":1411893,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a47ed90f44be26aab8df940df0c6757d40b79929","tid":1411893,"uid":17812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">所有啟勝管理嘅屋苑都應該問吓自己管理處 </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"召喚所有啟勝管理嘅居苑住戶<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaishing.hk%2Fresident%2Fkaishing%2Fcontact_us.do%3Fcompany%3Dkaishing&d=UCNXK7Cjp0Jh61Qt1camEK0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=97d48680\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kaishing.hk/resident/kaishing/contact_us.do?company=kaishing</a><br />\n<br />\n本人想查詢啟勝對近日示威事件之處理手法。<br />\n昨日天盛苑（同屬啟勝管理）